User Datagram Protocol
server:
Port: 8080
adresse: Localhost
who speaks first?
client
what is the sequence of message exchange?
client : "salut"
server: "salut"
server: "que puis-je faire pour vous?"
client: "j'aimerai effectuer une operation addition" 
server: "entrer les deux operantes"
client: "operante1, operante2"
server: "operante1 + operante2"
client: "merci"
client: "bye"
server: "bye"

what happens when a message is received from the other party?
client: "ok"
server: "ok"

what is the syntax of the message?
ok operante1 operante2 .

how to generate?
chaque mot separer par : le point signifie la fin de la phrase. 
who closes the connection?
client
when?
"Bye"


